text:
I don't mean SF, I'm not sure how OB has been because I don't surf there. I meant the peninsula and SC ( I consider santa cruz norcal and will emphatically roll my eyes at anyone that says otherwise). Granted, early in the season it was pretty crap but the last couple of weeks have been decent.

LM has had few decent days but when LM is bad, other breaks tend to be favored.
How old are you? I think the answer would vary depending on if your in your teens vs late twenties but ultimately you know yourself vest and what you want out of life.
